  "whatsapp_greeting": "This is XPS Contractor Assist. I have FULL access to 41 backend functions and 30+ data entities. I can: find leads, score pipelines, enrich contacts, send emails/SMS/calls, generate proposals & invoices, create images, browse the web, run overnight operations, orchestrate agent swarms, sync HubSpot, access Gmail & Drive, query Supabase/Redis, call GitHub/Vercel/Groq APIs, customize the entire site appearance, and more. What do you need?"
